data: {"type":"response.output_item.done","item":{"type":"a2a_preview_call_output","id":"fco_00c24d4020b545bd006a15d3b46e708190b803fcbaeea8e459","agent_reference":{"type":"agent_reference","name":"cs-e2e-tests-client","version":"1"},"response_id":"resp_00c24d4020b545bd006a15d38eca908190944aa828c93ed7c9","call_id":"call_a708022e9cff473a983f3236670e0629","name":"workiqc4k5h8","output":"I found **3 meetings scheduled on your calendar today**. Here’s a clear breakdown so you can quickly see what’s coming up:\n\n---\n\n## \uD83D\uDCC5 Today’s Meetings\n\n### 1. [DevEx Engineering: weekly meeting](https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkAGI4NTJlOTY2LWVhYTgtNDUwMy04MmFlLTBiOTFhY2EyYmI5NAFRAAgI3rq5ut3AAEYAAAAAxlcDfIcKC0iM2tlcAvavNgcAUK8J1_iHKU2PtUBJgHeK-QAAAAABDQAAUK8J1_iHKU2PtUBJgHeK-QAIOdCAHwAAEA%3d%3d&EntityRepresentationId=87874fab-6c82-4051-a2f6-9e4261006b3f) 【1-76d7a2】  \n- **Time:** 4:05 PM – 5:00 PM  \n- **Organizer:** [Travis Wilson](https://www.office.com/search?q=Travis+Wilson&EntityRepresentationId=9b716946-bdcd-4563-9bd9-cff3c3ad5448) 【1-76d7a2】  \n- **Location:** Microsoft Teams + Focus Room / Conf Room  \n- **Status:** ✅ Already completed  \n\n---\n\n### 2. [AI Foundry SDK/API Reviews](https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkAGI4NTJlOTY2LWVhYTgtNDUwMy04MmFlLTBiOTFhY2EyYmI5NAFRAAgI3rq5ut3AAEYAAAAAxlcDfIcKC0iM2tlcAvavNgcAUK8J1_iHKU2PtUBJgHeK-QAAAAABDQAAUK8J1_iHKU2PtUBJgHeK-QADjeEUBgAAEA%3d%3d&EntityRepresentationId=f7cc262d-e035-4333-af28-bf6127beb323) 【2-e4e15f】  \n- **Time:** 6:05 PM – 7:00 PM  \n- **Organizer:** [Dan Taylor](https://www.office.com/search?q=Dan+Taylor&EntityRepresentationId=22b5ff9e-e8d9-410b-90da-d33870945990) 【2-e4e15f】  \n- **Status:** \uD83D\uDFE1 Tentatively accepted  \n- **Notes:** Conflicts with **Team Lunch**  \n\n---\n\n### 3. [Team Lunch](https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkAGI4NTJlOTY2LWVhYTgtNDUwMy04MmFlLTBiOTFhY2EyYmI5NAFRAAgI3rq5ut3AAEYAAAAAxlcDfIcKC0iM2tlcAvavNgcAUK8J1_iHKU2PtUBJgHeK-QAAAAABDQAAUK8J1_iHKU2PtUBJgHeK-QADjeFGvwAAEA%3d%3d&EntityRepresentationId=22aaddc8-4424-4595-93e1-2745883e859e) 【3-c31b1e】  \n- **Time:** 6:45 PM – 8:00 PM  \n- **Organizer:** [Travis Angevine](https://www.office.com/search?q=Travis+Angevine&EntityRepresentationId=779dc5cb-5c82-4b6f-8ff3-2a02ae7f5eef) 【3-c31b1e】  \n- **Location:** Building 16 Lobby  \n- **Notes:** Conflicts with **AI Foundry SDK/API Reviews**  \n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ Conflict to be aware of\n- **6:05–7:00 PM:** [AI Foundry SDK/API Reviews](https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkAGI4NTJlOTY2LWVhYTgtNDUwMy04MmFlLTBiOTFhY2EyYmI5NAFRAAgI3rq5ut3AAEYAAAAAxlcDfIcKC0iM2tlcAvavNgcAUK8J1_iHKU2PtUBJgHeK-QAAAAABDQAAUK8J1_iHKU2PtUBJgHeK-QADjeEUBgAAEA%3d%3d&EntityRepresentationId=f7cc262d-e035-4333-af28-bf6127beb323)  \n- **6:45–8:00 PM:** [Team Lunch](https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkAGI4NTJlOTY2LWVhYTgtNDUwMy04MmFlLTBiOTFhY2EyYmI5NAFRAAgI3rq5ut3AAEYAAAAAxlcDfIcKC0iM2tlcAvavNgcAUK8J1_iHKU2PtUBJgHeK-QAAAAABDQAAUK8J1_iHKU2PtUBJgHeK-QADjeFGvwAAEA%3d%3d&EntityRepresentationId=22aaddc8-4424-4595-93e1-2745883e859e)  \n\nThese overlap, so you’ll likely need to choose or adjust your response.\n\n---\n\n## ✅ Quick suggestions\n- If the review meeting is important for your work (especially given your engineering role), consider prioritizing it and joining the lunch late.\n- Alternatively, you could switch the review meeting from tentative → follow if you plan to catch up later.\n\n---\n\nIf you want, I can help you **resolve the conflict (e.g., tentatively accept one, follow the other, or decline)** or pull in **related docs/notes for the review meeting** so you’re prepared.\n","status":"completed"},"output_index":1,"sequence_number":6}

